The carrier manifest for the order 124913 was generated in the first fulfilment batch of 12th January and the carrier manifest for the order 124961 was generated in the second fulfilment batch of 12th January (highlighted in screenshot shared below).&nbsp;
&nbsp;
You can download those carrier manifests and check once.
&nbsp;
Hope I was able to clarify this.
&nbsp;

&nbsp;
Thanks and Regards,
Sagar K S
Team PluginHive

