We have an update on your requirement.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
When an order is fulfilled in the plugin, for all the manifest pending orders along with the current order, the carrier will generate a manifest and all those orders will be marked as shipped in the plugin.
&nbsp;
The Canada Post manifest generation works on group of orders rather based on a single order.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
If the orders are marked as Fulfilled individually, it results in multiple manifests getting created.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
Considering your requirement, we will be bringing in an option to fulfill and transmit only selected orders for manifest generation. This enhancement would take sometime and we currently do not have an ETA for this.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
So, for time being, is it possible for you to generate labels for the orders only when they are ready to ship, so the manifest will be generated as per your requirement. Please give this a try for some orders and check the working. Let us know how it goes.
